That's about the only explanation I can find.  I doubt they changed anything concrete about the pet himself, but making him required 55+ level is sorta silly--I believe the lowest level a mage can be and complete the epic quest (or at least that I've seen) is 51.  Below that and I think you have trouble talking to some of the NPCs and doing turn-ins, but it isn't like many mages that have their epic are not going above 55 anyhow <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />
